---
import PitchLayout from '../../layouts/PitchLayout.astro';
---

<PitchLayout slug="distribution">
  <h1 class="slide-headline">Free tools and open source pull every developer&nbsp;in.</h1>

  <p class="slide-body-small" style="margin-bottom: 32px; color: var(--text-muted);">AI coding tools made strategy building accessible to anyone technical. These builders all need data, and free tools are how they find&nbsp;us.</p>

  <div class="flywheel-grid">
    <div class="card" style="opacity: 1; animation: none;">
      <div class="card-icon">&lt;/&gt;</div>
      <p class="card-label">Open source tools</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Free tools, sample notebooks, and open source packages that make it easy to get started. Every agent framework that imports our SDK is&nbsp;distribution.</p>
    </div>
    <span class="flywheel-grid-arrow">&rarr;</span>
    <div class="card" style="opacity: 1; animation: none;">
      <div class="card-icon">[0]</div>
      <p class="card-label">Free API tier</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Start building immediately. Live market data, basic historical, sample notebooks. Enough to test your first strategy without a credit&nbsp;card.</p>
    </div>
    <span class="flywheel-grid-arrow">&rarr;</span>
    <div class="card" style="opacity: 1; animation: none;">
      <div class="card-icon">[+]</div>
      <p class="card-label">Paid upgrade</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Historical depth, LOB snapshots, real-world source data. One agent making thousands of calls a day is worth more than a hundred casual&nbsp;users.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PitchLayout>
